1145.02 DISTRICT BOUNDARIES; ZONING MAP. (a) The boundaries of the districts are shown upon the map made a part of this Zoning Code, which map is designated as the \"Official Zoning Map\". The Zoning Map and all the notations, references, and other information shown thereon are a part of this Zoning Code and have the same force and effect as if the Zoning Map and all the notations, references, and other information shown thereon were all fully set forth or described herein, which Zoning Map is properly attested and is on file with the City Manager. (b) The fee for a copy of the City and Zoning Map shall be in accordance with the most current schedule of fees adopted by City Council. (Ord. 12-2012. Passed 10-15-12.)\n"} 
